tutorial: How to Set up a New Chart

definition.text: Let's take a look at your new working chart.  I hope you are as excited as I am!

paragraphs.text: First make sure to run all Data Tasks and wait for them to reach 100%.
Fire up the Charting Space and take a look at your Chart.  Have some fun and turn a few layers on and off.
If you can see layers showing up when you turn them on, great job! If nothing is showing up, go back over previous steps and make sure you didn't miss anything.
